  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The book \"Leaving Spain,\" published by Leuven University Press in 2022, demonstrates notable commercial reach as evidenced by its presence on platforms such as Amazon and Goodreads. The book's thematic alignment with sustainability principles indicates its relevance to ongoing policy discussions.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">\"Leaving Spain\" is a distinctive scholarly work released by Leuven University Press in 2022, which showcases its potential in the academic and commercial landscapes. While the book does not have citation metrics or mentions in high-fidelity community discourse, it is actively linked to commercial platforms like Amazon and Goodreads, reflecting its potential influence on public and academic audiences alike.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The inferred role of the book as a resource with policy sustainability relevance is highlighted by its association with one of the Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs). This demonstrates the author's intent to contribute meaningfully to discussions surrounding sustainable practices and social policies. Although the metrics indicate an absence of direct academic citations, the book's commercial positioning may facilitate broader discussions about its content.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Additionally, the lack of events, community mentions, or online interactions does not detract from its inherent academic value, as the absence of such data could also indicate a nascent phase of engagement. The academic discourse around \"Leaving Spain\" may still develop as it reaches more diverse audiences and generates interest across various sectors.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">In summary, while \"Leaving Spain\" currently lacks extensive metrics tracking its academic footprint or public discourse, its foundational themes related to sustainability align it with significant societal issues. As it gains visibility and engagement, there is potential for the book to contribute to broader conversations that intersect academic research and public awareness, ultimately fulfilling its role as a scholarly output of relevance.</p>",
